@swordofray

I think you might be posting in the comments for the wrong torrent. There are no bi/cue files in this one, just a .7z file to unzip with latest WinRAR or 7-zip, the .nfo file and a URL shortcut. You don't install anything.. just unzip.. double-click the reg file and play.

I haven't been able to get this to run in Vista 64-bit, but noticed as I was uninstalling that not all the registry keys merged properly, (HKCU worked but HKLM was missing) so I'll have to try again later. If not can someone recommend something more recent?
